<H1> Smooth Finite Elements Based on Powell-Sabin Triangle Split Triangles
</H1>

by Peter Alfeld and Larry Schumaker.

<H3>Abstract</H3>

Macro elements of smoothness <em>C<sup>r</sup></em> are constructed on Powell Sabin triangle splits for all r &geq; 0.  In
contrast to earlier constructions, our elements depend only on natural
derivative information.  




